      <title>Coinbase 的 Haas 在股价下跌后表示“加密货币又迎来了一天”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/coinbase-s-haas-says-just-another-day-in-crypto-after-stock-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Coinbase Global Inc. 首席财务官阿莱西亚·哈斯 (Alesia Haas) 为该加密货币交易所不断上升的费用和数字资产行业的波动性辩护，尽管该公司第一季度业绩好于预期，但该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/coinbase-s-haas-says-just-another-day-in-crypto-after-stock-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:03:09 GMT</pubDate>
